Class DataLoader

java.lang.Object
data.DataLoader
public class DataLoader extends Object
This class provides methods to load data from CSV files and populate the corresponding objects for applicants, projects, officers, managers, applications, and enquiries in the system.

    • loadProjects

      public static List<Project> loadProjects(String filePath, List<HDBOfficer> allOfficers, List<HDBManager> allManagers) throws IOException
      Loads projects from a CSV file, including related officers and managers.
      Parameters:
      filePath - The path to the CSV file.
      allOfficers - List of all HDB Officers in the system.
      allManagers - List of all HDB Managers in the system.
      Returns:
      A list of Projects loaded from the CSV file.
      Throws:
      IOException - If an I/O error occurs during file reading.
